Graphical Asynchronous Music Player Client
========================

GAMPC is an MPD client written in Python/Gtk+.


Requirements
------------

- Python 2 or 3
- PyGObject
- GLib 2.42 GObject Introspection
- Gtk+ 3.14 GObject Introspection
- Python modules:

  * ampd (Asynchronous Music Player Client)
  * apsw
